<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Heap on 魔都水滴</title><link>https://blog.margrop.net/tag/heap/</link><description>Recent content in Heap on 魔都水滴</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Mar 2021 09:54:54 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.margrop.net/tag/heap/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>gperftools安装与使用分析java堆外内存</title><link>https://blog.margrop.net/post/gperftools-install-analysis-memory-out-of-heap/</link><pubDate>Tue, 30 Mar 2021 09:54:54 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.margrop.net/post/gperftools-install-analysis-memory-out-of-heap/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="centos"&gt;CentOS&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;使用 yum 安装&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;yum install gperftools libunwind
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;可选，PDF 支持&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;yum install graphviz
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;设置环境变量&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;export LD_PRELOAD&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;/usr/lib64/libtcmalloc.so
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;export HEAPPROFILE&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;/DATA1/admin_tmp/gzip
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>